headline: Will Hershey Company (HSY) Maintain its Leadership Position?
summary: GreensKeeper Asset Management, an investment management company, released its fourth quarter investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The Value Fund finished 2024 +23.6% net of fees and expenses, which is slightly above the S&P/TSX +21.7% return, broadly in line with the DJIA +24.8% and trailing the S&P500 +35.7%. In addition, […]
